{"tid":151563,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"賣旗","createTime":"2017-03-11T03:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T04:12:17.000Z","uid":54713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26bd20dc9ab8a8fbfbc8af9a39134e32bc6281dc","tid":151563,"uid":54713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T03:37:30.000Z","msg":"你地星期六早上出街咪會見到好多（賣旗）活動嘅。好多時其實都唔知幫咗邊個機構賣旗，有時喺街到見到好多都喺賣旗都唔知真定假，所以好多時我都喺直行直過🤷🏼&zwj;♀️🤷🏼&zwj;♀️<br />\n簡單資訊:<br />\n      賣旗活動以往只限星期六上午進行，每一團體可在香港島、九龍和新界進行賣旗活動，但隨著慈善機構的增多，政府將賣旗活動進行日子增添為逢星期三和星期六，規模較大的慈善機構（如香港公益金）可在全香港進行賣旗活動。2005年開始，賣旗時間為上午7時至下午12時30分。（複製至維基，<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh/賣旗籌款）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh%2F%E8%B3%A3%E6%97%97%E7%B1%8C%E6%AC%BE%EF%BC%89&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=9450d5c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh/賣旗籌款）</a><br />\n<br />\n已獲政府於指定日子批准的賣旗機構:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.swd.gov.hk/doc/Control_of_Char/FD%20list%2016-17_20160516_1.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Fdoc%2FControl_of_Char%2FFD%2520list%252016-17_20160516_1.pdf&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=1b348126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.swd.gov.hk/doc/Control_of_Char/FD%20list%2016-17_20160516_1.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2017年3月18日:<br />\n  港島區: 國際四方福音會香港教區有限公司<br />\n                資料: <a href=\"http://www.wisegiving.org.hk/tc/donation/search/ngodetails.aspx?ID=17&amp;page=report\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wisegiving.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fdonation%2Fsearch%2Fngodetails.aspx%3FID%3D17%26page%3Dreport&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=4c1a0eb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.wisegiving.org.hk/tc/donation/search/ngodetails.aspx?ID=17&amp;page=report</a><br />\n  九龍區: 香港單親協會<br />\n                 資料: <a href=\"http://www.hkspa.org.hk/a-list/8725-cht\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkspa.org.hk%2Fa-list%2F8725-cht&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=3b3df797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkspa.org.hk/a-list/8725-cht</a><br />\n  新界區: 南葵涌社會服務處 <br />\n                  資料: <a href=\"http://www.skcsc.org.hk/skcsc/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.skcsc.org.hk%2Fskcsc%2Findex.php&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=54ab52a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.skcsc.org.hk/skcsc/index.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 無聊做下資料搜集 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3080971e0efbad0d92213e3b2a5d1b6d527dc974","tid":151563,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T04:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擺粒膠響度以為笑人巧威威<br />\n<br />\n但乜point都冇提出<br />\n<br />\n憑咩去話人<br />\n<br />\n尤其是係呢d真係正經討論ge post<br />\n<br />\n真係想見到大家有誠意咁去就一個題目發表自己意見<br />\n<br />\n唔係擺粒膠響度&hellip;自命清高咁笑人"}]}